Hello 0.7.3

Deprecated ``Trie.read`` and ``Trie.write``

The API would be cleaner without them, because a) they only work on
real files and will fail on e.g. ``ByteIO`` and b) they can be replaced
by ``load`` and ``save`` in 90% of the cases.
